A Warrior of Rellekka can be found wandering around in the city of Rellekka. They fight using melee, hitting quickly and usually hard. They have low defence but a decent amount of hitpoints, making them reasonable training targets, though their drops aren't very desirable.

They have the exact same appearance, stats, and drops as the Fremennik market guards, except they wield warhammers instead of Fremennik blades.
